data.DESCRIPT: Builder for an ALV grid based on CDS annotations

data.TYPESRC:
BEGIN OF ty_field_properties,
             fieldname           TYPE fieldname,
             fieldtype           TYPE zcds_alv_field_type,
             is_key              TYPE abap_bool,
             label               TYPE string,
             quickinfo           TYPE string,
             is_email            TYPE abap_bool,
             hidden              TYPE abap_bool,
             technical           TYPE abap_bool,
             default_aggregation TYPE string,
             position            TYPE i,
             is_hotspot          TYPE abap_bool,
             has_value_help      TYPE abap_bool,
             is_editable         TYPE abap_bool,
           END OF ty_field_properties
ty_field_properties_table TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF ty_field_properties WITH EMPTY KEY

BEGIN OF ty_ui_annotation,
             index TYPE sytabix,
             key   TYPE string,
             value TYPE string,
           END OF ty_ui_annotation
ty_ui_annotations TYPE SORTED TABLE OF ty_ui_annotation WITH NON-UNIQUE KEY index
